{"tid":1085573,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"痔瘡 有效醫治","createTime":"2019-03-31T08:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T16:35:39.000Z","uid":196776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea48a7fa50a06121fd7f86ca57fc7cf582ff3bf6","tid":1085573,"uid":196776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T08:53:27.000Z","msg":"好多人都有痔瘡煩惱，我最近因工作長期對電腦14 15個鐘，所以翻發，又痕又谷住，以前去醫生度電過，都萬幾蚊，上網看好多都係話坐熱水，不過我冇時間一日坐3次咁多，所以我轉用暖手包試下，訓覺就夾住訓，真係有效，仲可以長時間用，連續夾左三晚訓，粒肉細左好多，我打算長期夾住訓，睇下會唔會斷尾，再report比大家知。"},{"pid":"cc0d1f2f2bc992546f3e7f4534b828ad83fa4213","tid":1085573,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"Report呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暖手包夾住好撚熱架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac08109c0375bfbb0e366262320af1c4e3984625","tid":1085573,"uid":2533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"人地敷冰你敷暖包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}